She walked down the hall towards the room where Iron Raptor was.  She 
walked in and lowered her head as she passed the other males.  She 
went up to Iron Raptor. "I...I have the CR ready for your friends 
when you get them.  I'll be able to repair them no matter what 
condition they may be in."  She looked down and wanted to say she was 
tryijng to get over her fears, but thought better of it. 

She looked at Iron Raptor and then turned to leave.  She looked at 
the other males in the room as she walked past them.  She lowered her 
head as she past by Prowl. She stopped and spoke to Prowl, but didn't 
look him in the face. "I'll go and help with the rescue if you want 
me to.  If not, then I can still run the med lab when you return."  
She shook slightly.  She showed she was having to fight back her fear 
just to stand there and talk to him.
